<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4590595>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 6. Halicyclops ariakensis new species, female. (A) Habitus, dorsal; (B) urosome, dorsal; (C) urosome with right caudal ramus, ventral; (D) right caudal ramus, dorsal; (E) middle caudal setae; (F) antennule, ventral; (G) antenna, anterior; (H) mandible, anterior; (I) maxillule, medial; (J) palp of maxillule; (K) maxilla, anterior. A, non-type from Kashimagawa River; B–D, F–K, holotype; E, non-type from Shiota-gawa River." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4590595/files/figure.png" .

